body:
Hopefully at one point in the new season, Healers like {{champion:40}} {{champion:10}} {{champion:267}} {{champion:76}} {{champion:37}} {{champion:16}} 
will still be relevant next to the rest of their team and receive more AP/Armor itemization specifically tied to supporting (maybe even more personal items) in order to counter the rise of burst that began long before the new season was even announced.

To make a case, I watched a streamer get actually bursted 100-0 twice by a KhaZix, and later on that same KhaZix was able to jump around base scoring the &quot;Ace&quot; while not losing much health from the Towers that were still up during the base fight. If Assasssins are allowed to get too out of control, Healers and even Mages of both lanes will quickly become irrelevant and be replaced with ranged champions building Bruiser instead of building around their kits.
